		<RichText x="66" y="769" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="47" height="26" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蚀破：</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="602" width="508" height="154" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">在「祝祷」期间内展开持续13s的次数盾，其厚度为<span color="#a3a5fe">53</span><span>次；每次</span><span color="#ffffbf">元素攻击</span><span>可削减该护盾</span><span color="#ffccbf">1</span><span>点，</span><span color="#bfdfff">带有夜魂性质的攻击</span><span>则削减</span><span color="#ffccbf">3</span><span>点，没有冷却；击破后，摹结株将瘫痪12s。<br/></span><span color="#bfffbf">(N4) </span><span>次数盾厚度为</span><span color="#a3a5fe">72</span><span>次，且不再衰减。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>非「祝祷」期间常驻厚度为</span><span color="#a3a5fe">150</span><span>次次数盾，击破后依照次数盾所承受伤害造成一次高额真伤，由</span><span color="#ffdfbf">60%夜魂总伤+10%非夜魂总伤</span><span>构成，不超过摹结株</span><span color="#ffdfbf">30%</span><span>的生命值。<br/>击破后的瘫痪时间延长至18s；次数盾Gap为20s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<Rect x="576" y="32" width="768" height="768" alpha="1" visible="false" blendMode="normal" radiusX="0" radiusY="0">
			<fill>
