		<RichText x="1538" y="320" width="444" height="87" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">持有<span textDecoration="underline">虚界力护罩</span><span>的一段时间后</span><span color="#ffdfbf">(60s)</span><span>时，摹结株将枝节插入地面进行蓄力，并持续在场地内召唤幽生蓟，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>(</span><span color="#99ff99">10</span><span>级「</span><span textDecoration="underline">蚀破</span><span>」)；13s后蓄力完成，产生大爆炸，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">秒杀我方当前场上角色。</span><span>该技能不会重置虚界力护罩。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
